    <h2 class="title"><a href="http://www.theverge.com/2014/1/30/5363096/box-has-reportedly-filed-for-an-ipo-in-secret">Box has reportedly filed for an IPO in secret</a></h2>
    
    <div class="byline clearfix">
      <div class="floatL">
        <a href="http://www.theverge.com/users/CaseyNewton" class="author">Casey Newton</a>
        January  30, 2014 08:37 pm
      </div>
      
        <div class="floatR"><a href="http://www.theverge.com/2014/1/30/5363096/box-has-reportedly-filed-for-an-ipo-in-secret#comments" class="comment-count  heat1">5</a></div>
      
